<div class="language-zeile line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="shiki" data-ext="zeile" style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#abb2bf;--shiki-light-bg:#FAFAFA;--shiki-dark-bg:#282c34"><pre class="shiki shiki-themes one-light one-dark-pro vp-code" v-pre=""><code class="language-zeile"><span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">Background.</span><span style="--shiki-light:#4078F2;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF">change</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">(</span><span style="--shiki-light:#4078F2;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF">to</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">: </span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379">"scenario102/bg01021.png"</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">)</span></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>这里的“scenario102/bg01021.png”是一个<em>路径</em>，用于唯一地定位一个资源。
